PTHREAD_MUTEX_ERRORCHECK does not understand pthread_cond_wait 

pthread_cond_wait can lock and unlock mutexes but does not update the untrusted 
lock state, which confuses the error checking lock. This patch teaches 
pthread_cond_wait how to update the untrusted lock state. 

BUG=http://code.google.com/p/nativeclient/issues/detail?id=1177
Original patch by Eric Seidel. 

Review URL: http://codereview.chromium.org/5266006
